For the new slimmer blog design introduced in CONF-18738:

The controls are at the bottom, below the list of blog posts for the month.

They should be at the top instead, so that the position is unaffected by the number of blogs. In months with lots of blog posts, the users may have to scroll down to find the controls with the current design.

