I am unable to find the short name of a Space anywhere. I gave up after searching around for almost 10 minutes. It is not on the Tools->Info, nor on the main page of the Space, nor in the Browse Space.

When I want to link to a page in a different Space, what I usually do is find some other page which is already linking there, and copy the name from there.

Stuff like this should be easy and obvious to find.

