The [Did You Mean|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Enabling+the+Did+You+Mean+Feature] feature documentation and Confluence interface should state which English locale is required for it to work.
Language packs such as English (US) do not allow this feature to work and can cause users confusion.
